<item>
            <title>[HBASE-1535] Add client ability to perform mutations without the WAL</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1535</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are a number of cases where a client might not want/need its edits to be written into the HLog.  The most obvious use of this would be during a bulk import where we want the best performance possible and data loss is acceptable (can rerun the import).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Does this become a flag on Put or a special mode of HTable?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12428172">HBASE-1535</key>
